{"id": "1453056295115423906", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1382682733074972694", "author_name": "sakiiia_0952", "author_bot": false, "content": "基礎的な事なんですが触腕ダメージボーナスって、触腕にどんな影響を与えるんですか？", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T16:06:57.236000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1453057070961135868", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "495956549777489921", "author_name": "lynne2830", "author_bot": false, "content": "分かりにくいんですけど、逆なんですよね\n触腕ダメージを元に追加ボーナスが発生する、系です", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T16:10:02.212000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1453057297206083584", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1382682733074972694", "author_name": "sakiiia_0952", "author_bot": false, "content": "触腕ダメージボーナスがあると触腕ダメージの増え方が変わるみたいな感じですかね...？", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T16:10:56.153000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1453057503016255679", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "495956549777489921", "author_name": "lynne2830", "author_bot": false, "content": "具体的に何のキャラ使ってます？", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T16:11:45.222000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1453057680682778665", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1382682733074972694", "author_name": "sakiiia_0952", "author_bot": false, "content": "トゥルーですね\n攻撃の触腕ダメージボーナスが150%となってるんですがよく分かってなくて", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T16:12:27.581000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1453058168744575178", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "495956549777489921", "author_name": "lynne2830", "author_bot": false, "content": "例えば触腕の数値が40あるとしたら、攻撃札に40＊150％のボーナスが付与されます", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T16:14:23.944000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1453058640826339458", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "力ダメージボーナスも同じタイプ", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T16:16:16.497000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1453058846041051347", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "495956549777489921", "author_name": "lynne2830", "author_bot": false, "content": "攻撃札の20ダメージ＋（触腕ダメージ40＊1.5）の60で80ダメージ与える感じで\n触腕の強化ではないんですよね", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T16:17:05.424000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1453059133858385921", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1382682733074972694", "author_name": "sakiiia_0952", "author_bot": false, "content": "なるほど、ありがとうございます！", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T16:18:14.045000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1453059424322195619", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1382682733074972694", "author_name": "sakiiia_0952", "author_bot": false, "content": "なんかトゥルーの攻撃のカードだけ300とかダメージ出るなーと思ってたらそう言う事なんですね...", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T16:19:23.297000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1453059700634423339", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "495956549777489921", "author_name": "lynne2830", "author_bot": false, "content": "触腕育てばびっくりするくらい強くなりますねー", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T16:20:29.175000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1453060721817551081", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "1382682733074972694", "author_name": "sakiiia_0952", "author_bot": false, "content": "それにしてもトゥルーが強いというのがよくわかりますね\n10ターン経過する頃には触腕ダメージ1200とかなってて驚きます", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T16:24:32.644000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1453061447612370944", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "495956549777489921", "author_name": "lynne2830", "author_bot": false, "content": "出だしの遅さだけがネックですけど、いつの間にか意味分かんないダメージ出すので楽しいですねｗ", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T16:27:25.687000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
